headline: Enphase Energy (ENPH) Posts Strong Q3 Results While Europe Demand Softens and Q4 Guidance Falls
summary: Enphase Energy Inc. (NASDAQ:ENPH) ranks among the best sustainability stocks to invest in. Enphase Energy Inc. (NASDAQ:ENPH) reported third-quarter results on October 28 that came in higher than analysts predicted, while its fourth-quarter revenue guidance turned out lower than expected. The company’s third-quarter adjusted earnings per share of $0.90 greatly exceeded the $0.64 analyst expectation. […]
